## Shared Schemas

```ts
const seoSchema = z.object({
  metaTitle: z.string().optional(),
  metaDescription: z.string().optional(),
  ogImage: z.string().optional(),
});

const metricSchema = z.object({
  value: z.string(),
  label: z.string(),
});
```

