| Field | Notes |
|---|---|
| `logo` | Path to SVG logo in `public/` (e.g. `/logos/boeing.svg`) |
| `order` | Sort order ascending. Default `0` |

### Testimonials (YAML)

```ts
const testimonials = defineCollection({
  loader: contentLoader({
    extensions: ["yaml"],
    base: "src/content/testimonials",
